title: Clay Shooter - April 2016
description:
English | 64 pages | PDF | 38.8 MB

Clay Shooter provides all the news, views and features that a clay shooting enthusiast needs to keep up to date with what's happening on the clay circuit. Our news pages contain all the latest from the shooting associations, charity events, and our top shooters' successes in international competitions as well as practical advice on subjects like choke, ribs, cartridges, as well as advanced instruction to help you improve your scores
